                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-131-off712 t18240715-131-cd713"></join>, two shirts, value 16 s.; a shift, value 6 s.; a tablecloth, value 4 s. 6 d.; a waistcoat, value 7 s.; two pairs of stockings, value 2 s.; a neckerchief, value 2 s.; four towels, value 2 s.; four aprons, value 4 s.; a frill, value 6 d.; two caps, value 4 s. 8 d.; a night gown, value 3 s. 6 d.; another gown, value 14 s.; an apron, value 1 s., and a basket, value 18 d.
